query:
SELECT
                    slot_index as "index: _",
                    value as "value: _"
                    FROM neo_account_slots
                    WHERE account_address = $1
                    AND slot_index = $2
                    AND block_number = (SELECT MAX(block_number)
                                            FROM historical_slots
                                            WHERE account_address = $1
                                            AND idx = $2
                                            AND block_number <= $3)
